{"type": "article", "id": 16287, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2015-10-20T06:32:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 17437, "name": "Stoft"}, {"id": 17438, "name": "杜邦™"}, {"id": 17439, "name": "Kovac Family"}, {"id": 17440, "name": "M2Malletier"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 17441, "name": "Hong Ying Guo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 91, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003457lOygxDzUEkGpJAF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h3>\r\n\tPillow Stool by Hong Ying Guo\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这把用钢铁做的椅子有一个两层的座位，勾勒出像枕头一样的弯曲弧度，冲淡了钢铁本身的金属感，给人舒服和放松的感受。上下两层的铁棒方向相反，重叠看上去就像交织成网格，光从不同方向照射过来，能投射出不同形状的网格纹路，且富有变化。此外，两层中间空间也是放杂志的好地方。<a href=\"http://www.hongyingguo.com/71945/632231/work/pillow-stool\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215238zIMurtjHAFZcvxgP.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215238e18X92ckru6QiEwp.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215239Ls6Sf3ZKjq5aA2e7.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215239qo0EJ2GyZsaHXm9p.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215240jFinuC940vKEGBVl.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tBiophilia by Stoft\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这套瓷器包括四个部分，黑色的碗“Capsula”代表了子房，白色的有褶皱边的花瓶是主干，灰色的细长“Truncus”是分支，上面放着装饰用的陶器 “Spore”是孢子。四个部分暗示了植物的生根发展过程，可以单独作为花瓶，或是叠加在一起。它们本身的故事性让这个设计充满活力。<a href=\"http://dennyakartan.tictail.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215240j8IY4Me6kWUu9B2D.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.64142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215240tG2lcsTEZmA9yRMq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052152412Urh1OVl7qyLgsDe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215241fun0I24695oEpyRZ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143611Jk6oW9iEH1FbjcTu.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t25 Lamp by Kovac Family\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这盏灯的木质灯罩由 25 片组成，因而名叫 25 Lamp ，来自瑞典的 Kovac Family。每一片都在灯泡上面的连接处固定，依次拉开形成一个球体，层层相叠，是一个有层次感的灯笼。光照强度能通过灯罩的开合做调整，看似传统，却很有现代的设计感。灯罩是手工做的，可以选择橡树、白蜡木和桦树。<a href=\"http://store.kovacfamily.com/collections/numbers/products/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052152428oBhVDskL2F3RnuM.gif\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"gif\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215245zkZ640HTSx72NQRE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.37486574\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215246j8YEN1l3mRaInoGC.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215247EX04GuMLzUfI1Avk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215247b9zNIUuBTO7wFrGe.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t无线充电可丽耐® 面板 by 杜邦™ \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t杜邦™建筑公司与 Power Matters Alliance（无线充电联盟，简称 PMA）合作，推出这款融入无线充电技术的可丽耐® 面板。利用电感耦合在两个面板之间的非接触式感应充电，只需把手机放在特殊标明的可丽耐®面板上，无需插线，就能实现充电。如果这项技术得到推广，那么公共空间如机场、餐厅等地的充电问题就能得到解决。<a href=\"http://www.dupont.co.uk/bi/charging-surfaces/home.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215248URe0NiXYDcK3HOmf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215249aQpFs5R6DOgX3qwJ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.31662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215249pua9qSe0FvMZr5my.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215250RjTZQsP1yV7SlDIX.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215250zq2bvTDphJySBkQw.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\t2016 春夏手袋系列 by M2Malletier \r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这是 M2Malletier 推出的新款手包，这个品牌是由哥伦比亚的两个女生 Melissa Losada 和 Marcela Velez 自创的。她们热爱使用金属杆的手把，与皮质包对比，极简而有个性。新款更大胆采用不同颜色与形状的材料，给女生的穿搭提供不同选择。另外，皮质本身的花纹也让皮包有了质感，不会因极简而显得无聊。<a href=\"http://www.m2malletier.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是她们的主页。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215255X60oOepPwGvcT1nq.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215256W0YoCVOKxi6gfmrQ.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215303B5VJr7XmkqF3bSZ1.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215303ojWuq197AZUKTwJ5.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153047M8r09xeJDNSkFoI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215304iL6lIWVXAPEbZrSD.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143611AuJf1ZK40b2r5ESP.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215305cOTQi0U76FKVbt3R.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<h3>\r\n\tPayaa by NikeLab\r\n</h3>\r\n<p>\r\n\tNikeLab 发布了秋季新品 Payaa，灵感源于阿拉斯加原住民的 Payaaqek 靴。大面积采用透气的网眼布料，坡形的橡胶底和抽绳鞋带让鞋子舒适透气，在橡胶底的侧面用浮雕做标志，很帅气。有黑、白、桃红和蓝色四种，售价 80 美元，<a href=\"http://store.nike.com/us/en_us/pd/nikelab-payaa-unisex-shoe/pid-10327657/pgid-11100533\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052153065jviGVL7x1rAfloW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215308BxUmWJKRCZgOYkMj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.20754717\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215309RSUner3TpzL0a1ty.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215310KUXPWZrskgFq2N7Q.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.60708263\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605215311kRKG5xbl2aLOFo9Q.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56027165\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n"}